flowRoot.flowPara: As a younger person one has almost no possibility to store evidence in a way the older criminals can not find or delete. Especially if you would have an eye1 card they would know where you hide things. But if you have for example a big library you could take an SD-Card (i dont trust SD-Cards) or an USB Stick and take of the housing, then you can put that in a book from a library. If you close your eyes and select a random book you dont even know by your own then it is stored and even you would have to search a while until you have the stick back, but the older criminals would have to search too. If they know about that, they maybe start to search too, but then you can prove that they are actively searching for evidence, so you can call the police and make your case.
